nee thanda kanike ( kannada : ನೀ ತಂದ ಕಾಣಿಕೆ ) is a 1985 indian kannada film , directed by dwarakish and produced by dwarakish . the film stars vishnuvardhan , girish karnad , jayasudha and c. r. simha in lead roles . the film had musical score by vijayanand . it is a remake of the hindi hit film sharaabi ( 1984 ) starring amitabh bachchan and jayaprada which itself was loosely based on the 1981 american movie arthur .